RTAI-Lab Installation
=====================

- Compile and install the Mesa library

1)  Download Mesa:

http://cgit.freedesktop.org/mesa/mesa/snapshot/mesa-8.0.5.tar.gz

2)  Untar the archive:

tar zxf mesa-8.0.5.tar.gz

3)  cd mesa-8.0.5

4)  ./configure --prefix=/usr --enable-static

5)  make

6)  make install

- Compile and install the EFLTK package

7)  Download EFLTK:

sourceforge.net/projects/ede/files/efltk/2.0.8/efltk-2.0.8.tar.gz

8)  cd efltk

9)  ./configure --prefix=/usr/local --enable-xdbe --enable-opengl --enable-threads

10) ./emake

11) Install as superuser or root:

make install

12) Run ldconfig as superuser or root:

ldconfig